stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> QUEUED: POST /api/v1/executions
  QUEUED --> RUNNING: worker claim_next_queued()
  RUNNING --> COMPLETED: valuation COMPLETED + memo COMPLETED + pdf exists
  RUNNING --> FAILED: valuation FAILED
  RUNNING --> FAILED: memo COMPLETED_WITH_MEMO_FAILURE
  RUNNING --> FAILED: unhandled exception

  FAILED --> RUNNING: manual recovery script (optional)
  RUNNING --> COMPLETED: mark_completed after successful recovery

  note right of QUEUED
    Row inserted with:
    status=QUEUED
    submitted_at_utc
    generated run_id
  end note

  note right of RUNNING
    started_at_utc set once
    worker executes valuation then memo
  end note

  note right of COMPLETED
    finished_at_utc set
    spreadsheet_url present
    memo_pdf_path present
    error_message cleared
  end note

  note right of FAILED
    finished_at_utc set
    error_message records merged context:
    valuation_status + memo_status + notes
  end note
